nodes.text: Tracey Eddon (born November 3, 1958) was the C-3PO stunt double for Anthony Daniels and the Princess Leia stunt double for Carrie Fisher in Star Wars: Episode VI Return of the Jedi.
Eddon has done stunt work for many films including Mission: Impossible and GoldenEye.
